      "type": "text",
      "x": 440,
      "y": 430,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 20,
      "fill": "#2f9e44",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "strokeWidth": 0,
      "text": "时间复杂度",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": "Arial",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "aBcDeGA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 440,
      "y": 460,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 120,
      "fill": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "strokeWidth": 0,
      "text": "理想情况 (均匀分布):\n  get/put: O(1)\n\n最坏情况 (全部碰撞):\n  get/put: O(n)\n\n实际环境:\n  get/put: O(1) ~ O(log n)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": "Arial",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "aBcDeGB",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 660,
      "y": 420,
